254
00:12:30,586 --> 00:12:32,245
Ti trovo in gran forma, sai, sei proprio...

255
00:12:34,057 --> 00:12:35,238
Sì, sì, lo so, lo so.

256
00:12:35,998 --> 00:12:38,801
