807
00:42:23,938 --> 00:42:24,297
Stai bene?

808
00:42:24,318 --> 00:42:24,797
Stai bene?

809
00:42:50,414 --> 00:42:51,635
Ciao Corrado.

810
00:42:51,655 --> 00:42:53,896
Sto aspettando ancora la ricetta del tiramisù.

811
00:42:54,177 --> 00:42:55,717
Va bene, te la porto domani.

812
00:43:00,221 --> 00:43:00,681
Tutto bene.

813
00:43:10,668 --> 00:43:10,947
Ciao.

814
00:43:12,268 --> 00:43:12,710
Com'è andata?

815
00:43:13,929 --> 00:43:14,391
Ho dormito.

816
00:43:16,264 --> 00:43:16,784
